1
00:00:02,220 --> 00:00:06,870
Kerah kami ditarik, dan diberi bogem mentah

2
00:00:07,090 --> 00:00:11,730
sehingga kami sempoyongan,
lalu jongkok bersebelahan

3
00:00:11,880 --> 00:00:16,560
Di tengah hujan yang diprediksi,
kau menyeringai

4
00:00:16,820 --> 00:00:22,400
lalu berbohong bahwa "luka pasti akan sembuh"

5
00:00:22,840 --> 00:00:25,420
Bahkan adu mulut yang sering dilakukan

6
00:00:26,090 --> 00:00:30,660
tak bisa kulakukan dengan baik

7
00:00:30,820 --> 00:00:35,720
Jangan katakan candaan
yang membosankan

8
00:00:35,960 --> 00:00:40,970
Rasa bosannya pun tampak jelas di mataku!

9
00:00:41,030 --> 00:00:48,670
Tak peduli walau seberapa banyak air
mata yang mengaliri pipi lebamku ini

10
00:00:48,720 --> 00:00:55,340
melalui hati yang goyah
bersanding dengan bahu

11
00:00:55,410 --> 00:00:59,900
kau pasti bisa menghindari
akhir buruk yang menghantui!

12
00:01:00,240 --> 00:01:05,470
Kenapa rasa sakit ini lebih
nyaman dibanding kebahagiaan?

13
00:01:05,580 --> 00:01:09,840
Bahkan rasa sakit ini kian menggema!

14
00:01:09,920 --> 00:01:14,480
Sambil menggigit lidah dan
mengenakan baju basah,

15
00:01:14,520 --> 00:01:17,690
mari kita tertawakan wajah sembap ini

16
00:01:18,060 --> 00:01:22,430
Lalu di tengah malam bermandikan hujan

17
00:01:22,880 --> 00:01:30,200
kita ikrarkan balas dendam!

18
00:01:31,550 --> 00:01:37,200
(#5 Melintasi Waktu Lagi)

19
00:01:32,509 --> 00:01:37,720
Hanagaki Takemichi.
Kamu dipecaaaaat.

20
00:01:38,270 --> 00:01:39,160
Eh?

21
00:01:39,220 --> 00:01:41,780
Jangan malah bilang "eh?"
Wajar saja kamu dipecat.

22
00:01:41,780 --> 00:01:43,780
Karena kamu bolos dua minggu,

23
00:01:44,120 --> 00:01:48,640
pikirmu siapa yang kena getaaaaahnya?

24
00:01:48,780 --> 00:01:49,800
Ma-Maaf.

25
00:01:49,820 --> 00:01:51,890
Pokoknya dipecaaaat!

26
00:01:52,490 --> 00:01:55,759
Oh, begitu.
Dua minggu sudah berlalu, ya.

27
00:01:56,240 --> 00:02:00,640
Kalau waktu di masa lalu berjalan,
di masa kini juga sama.

28
00:02:01,340 --> 00:02:03,160
Anu. Gajiku?

29
00:02:03,160 --> 00:02:04,950
Nanti ditransfer.

30
00:02:09,240 --> 00:02:10,910
Hei, Naoto.

31
00:02:11,070 --> 00:02:15,290
'Gimana kalau aku bilang pada Hina
tentang masa depannya?

32
00:02:15,460 --> 00:02:16,840
Seperti padamu saat itu.

33
00:02:16,860 --> 00:02:18,130
Ditolak.

34
00:02:18,340 --> 00:02:21,150
Takemichi. Kau mau
mencari jalan pintas, ya?

35
00:02:21,260 --> 00:02:23,090
Yah, aku enggak bermaksud begitu!

36
00:02:23,170 --> 00:02:27,120
Karena hidupku memang susah,
jadi aku enggak kepikiran cara mudah.

37
00:02:27,360 --> 00:02:29,270
Kalau kau disangka orang sinting,

38
00:02:29,510 --> 00:02:32,040
terus dibenci sama Kakakku, 'gimana?

39
00:02:32,070 --> 00:02:32,920
Eh?

40
00:02:33,100 --> 00:02:35,970
Wajarnya, orang takkan percaya
sama topik seperti itu.

41
00:02:36,110 --> 00:02:37,260
Kau bodoh, ya?

42
00:02:38,170 --> 00:02:42,850
Aku percaya padamu karena kebetulan
aku sedang kecanduan okultisme.

43
00:02:43,150 --> 00:02:46,160
Benar juga.
Pertimbanganmu bagus.

44
00:02:47,040 --> 00:02:48,870
Tapi kok disebut bodoh, sih?

45
00:02:49,130 --> 00:02:52,780
Sendou mati, dan kita tidak
bisa bertemu Sano.

46
00:02:53,220 --> 00:02:55,090
Berarti, demi menyelamatkan Kakakku,

47
00:02:55,090 --> 00:02:57,880
kau harus kembali ke masa lalu
dan mengubah Touman.

48
00:02:58,290 --> 00:03:00,840
Kembali ke awal, ya?

49
00:03:03,400 --> 00:03:06,060
Andai saja Draken masih hidup.

50
00:03:06,350 --> 00:03:08,150
Soal Ryuguji Ken, ya?

51
00:03:08,410 --> 00:03:09,260
Ya.

52
00:03:09,840 --> 00:03:11,380
Kau sudah menyelidikinya?

53
00:03:11,670 --> 00:03:12,460
Ya.

54
00:03:14,480 --> 00:03:16,079
Ini koran pada saat itu.

55
00:03:17,120 --> 00:03:18,910
3 Agustus 2005.

56
00:03:19,250 --> 00:03:22,329
Di parkiran Kuil Musashi,
distrik Shibuya, Tokyo,

57
00:03:22,440 --> 00:03:24,810
terjadi tawuran yang melibatkan
50 anggota geng motor.

58
00:03:25,190 --> 00:03:29,810
Lalu, seorang siswa kelas 3 SMP
ditusuk di perut dengan pisau,

59
00:03:30,360 --> 00:03:31,310
hingga tewas.

60
00:03:33,420 --> 00:03:36,620
Ada beberapa catatan lain
yang tersisa dari kasus itu.

61
00:03:37,050 --> 00:03:41,710
Selain itu, tampaknya penyebab Ryuguji
tewas karena adanya perseteruan ...

62
00:03:41,840 --> 00:03:44,060
... antara Kubu Draken
dan Kubu Mikey di Touman.

63
00:03:44,980 --> 00:03:46,960
Hah?
Tunggu dulu!

64
00:03:47,200 --> 00:03:50,290
3 Agustus itu 2 minggu lagi, 'kan?!

65
00:03:50,560 --> 00:03:52,520
Iya, 12 tahun lalu.

66
00:03:52,700 --> 00:03:56,820
Mikey dan Draken berseteru?
Pasti ada yang salah!

67
00:03:57,970 --> 00:04:01,360
Bisa dibilang, Bang Draken itu orang
yang paling mengerti Bang Mikey!

68
00:04:01,470 --> 00:04:04,430
Pokoknya, mereka tak mungkin berseteru!

69
00:04:04,660 --> 00:04:06,280
Mungkin ada motif tersembunyi.

70
00:04:06,470 --> 00:04:08,540
Eh? A-Aku kurang tahu ....

71
00:04:08,620 --> 00:04:11,500
Tapi, aku bisa memastikan bahwa
mereka tak mungkin berseteru!

72
00:04:11,790 --> 00:04:15,390
Namun, Ryuguji mati pada hari itu.

73
00:04:17,040 --> 00:04:18,350
Ayo selidiki.

74
00:04:18,519 --> 00:04:19,079
Ah.

75
00:04:19,160 --> 00:04:22,970
Hari ini 19 Juli.
Tenggat waktunya 2 pekan.

76
00:04:23,470 --> 00:04:28,490
Selidikilah penyebab kematiannya,
dan selamatkan Ryuguji Ken pada 3 Agustus.

77
00:04:28,990 --> 00:04:30,940
Itulah misimu kali ini!

78
00:04:32,030 --> 00:04:34,890
Sano Manjirou berubah
karena kematian Ryuguji Ken.

79
00:04:35,310 --> 00:04:38,720
Lalu, Sendou Atsushi yang bunuh diri
karena takut sama Kisaki Tetta.

80
00:04:39,409 --> 00:04:43,370
Serta, Tachibana Hinata dibunuh oleh
Touman yang jadi geng jahat saat ini,

81
00:04:43,850 --> 00:04:45,030
adalah Kakakku.

82
00:04:45,860 --> 00:04:49,600
Kalau misi ini berjalan lancar,
semuanya pasti bisa selamat!

83
00:04:49,900 --> 00:04:52,430
Baik Draken, Akkun,

84
00:04:52,830 --> 00:04:53,850
maupun Hina?

85
00:04:54,350 --> 00:04:55,220
Iya.

86
00:04:55,780 --> 00:04:58,080
Mantap banget ini mah.

87
00:04:59,550 --> 00:05:02,340
Aku pasti akan menyelamatkan Draken!

88
00:05:03,050 --> 00:05:04,750
Tolong, ya!

89
00:05:14,080 --> 00:05:15,120
Hah?

90
00:05:15,950 --> 00:05:17,230
Gelap!

91
00:05:19,190 --> 00:05:21,800
Kok kayaknya berat, ya?

92
00:05:22,200 --> 00:05:23,240
Hah?!

93
00:05:26,090 --> 00:05:27,830
Enggak boleh ciuman, loh.

94
00:05:29,050 --> 00:05:29,870
Heh?!

95
00:05:30,570 --> 00:05:32,890
Kenapa situasinya begini?!

96
00:05:33,430 --> 00:05:35,550
Enggak boleh ciuman?

97
00:05:35,840 --> 00:05:38,720
Terus menunya apa aja?!

98
00:05:41,150 --> 00:05:41,870
Eh?

99
00:05:48,070 --> 00:05:50,860
Iya. Tambah 30 menit lagi.

100
00:05:51,310 --> 00:05:52,800
Mau minum sesuatu?

101
00:05:53,930 --> 00:05:54,659
Loh?

102
00:05:57,670 --> 00:06:00,080
Apa?
Apa yang terjadi?!

103
00:06:03,340 --> 00:06:05,810
Ini beda banget dibanding
hidupku yang dulu!

104
00:06:05,970 --> 00:06:09,470
Perjaka abadi sepertiku hampir
enak-enak sama cewek seimut itu?!

105
00:06:10,300 --> 00:06:12,630
Aku harus merahasiakan ini dari Hina!

106
00:06:12,670 --> 00:06:13,310
Apa, tuh?

107
00:06:14,820 --> 00:06:16,440
HAH?!

108
00:06:16,480 --> 00:06:16,870
Eh?

109
00:06:16,890 --> 00:06:19,390
Hina?! Kenapa kamu di sini?!

110
00:06:19,430 --> 00:06:20,960
Aku pulang les.

111
00:06:21,120 --> 00:06:23,370
Kamu sendiri lagi apa?

112
00:06:23,390 --> 00:06:25,310
Yah! Eng ....

113
00:06:28,060 --> 00:06:28,710
Eh?

114
00:06:29,400 --> 00:06:32,600
Apa? Ada yang 'nempel?

115
00:06:35,090 --> 00:06:36,750
Mu-Mungkinkah ...

116
00:06:38,940 --> 00:06:40,500
... aku ketahuan?!

117
00:06:40,960 --> 00:06:44,430
Soal itu, bisa dibilang aku
enggak ingat apa-apa!

118
00:06:44,490 --> 00:06:45,900
Kamu bicara apa?

119
00:06:46,610 --> 00:06:47,420
Hah?

120
00:06:48,140 --> 00:06:50,930
Takemichi, kamu aneh belakangan ini.

121
00:06:51,100 --> 00:06:51,690
Eh?

122
00:06:51,880 --> 00:06:53,900
Hari ini Takemichi versi dewasa.

123
00:06:55,409 --> 00:06:59,790
Saat melihat kembang api di atap,
kamu buru-buru pulang.

124
00:06:59,990 --> 00:07:02,520
Bahkan di sekolah,
kamu kayak menghindariku.

125
00:07:03,680 --> 00:07:05,960
Tapi saat ini, kamu tampak baik hati.

126
00:07:06,930 --> 00:07:08,380
Oh, begitu.

127
00:07:08,570 --> 00:07:13,870
Setelah kembali ke 12 tahun mendatang,
aku yang di masa lalu tidak tahu apa-apa.

128
00:07:18,150 --> 00:07:20,090
Enggak boleh ciuman, loh.

129
00:07:20,440 --> 00:07:24,880
Terus kenapa bisa sampai kayak begitu?
Bodohnya diriku di masa lalu!

130
00:07:25,390 --> 00:07:27,360
Takemichi, ponselmu bunyi, tuh.

131
00:07:27,530 --> 00:07:28,320
Eh?

132
00:07:28,620 --> 00:07:29,530
Oh, iya.

133
00:07:31,300 --> 00:07:33,290
Loh, dari Bang Draken?

134
00:07:33,810 --> 00:07:34,760
Halo.

135
00:07:35,120 --> 00:07:37,680
Takemichi.
Kau lagi apa?

136
00:07:37,920 --> 00:07:39,790
Eh? Sekarang ....

137
00:07:39,820 --> 00:07:42,980
Datanglah ke Kuil Musashi sekarang juga.
Semuanya lagi kumpul.

138
00:07:43,070 --> 00:07:43,650
Eh?

139
00:07:43,880 --> 00:07:45,630
Ah, kalau sekarang ....

140
00:07:47,560 --> 00:07:51,110
Hina, aku dipanggil sama Bang Draken.

141
00:07:51,900 --> 00:07:53,470
Oke, Hina juga ikut!

142
00:07:53,970 --> 00:07:55,090
Seriusan?

143
00:07:55,300 --> 00:07:57,500
Dia temanmu, 'kan?

144
00:08:03,890 --> 00:08:05,060
Takemichi.

145
00:08:05,370 --> 00:08:06,190
Hm?

146
00:08:07,040 --> 00:08:10,540
Bagimu, apakah sesuatu
yang berharga itu?

147
00:08:10,810 --> 00:08:12,940
Eh? Sesuatu yang berharga?

148
00:08:16,040 --> 00:08:18,120
Momen seperti inilah
yang berharga bagi Hina.

149
00:08:18,380 --> 00:08:20,200
Tidak perlu melakukan apa-apa.

150
00:08:20,800 --> 00:08:25,070
Jalan berduaan seperti ini,
lalu membahas berbagai hal.

151
00:08:25,360 --> 00:08:27,980
Momen seperti ini bersamamu.

152
00:08:30,000 --> 00:08:32,460
Aku mau momen seperti ini
sebanyak-banyaknya!

153
00:08:33,169 --> 00:08:34,150
Momen ....

154
00:08:34,520 --> 00:08:35,630
Oh, iya.

155
00:08:35,950 --> 00:08:38,690
Bagiku yang berharga itu
adalah menyelamatkan Hina!

156
00:08:38,780 --> 00:08:41,929
Menyelamatkan Hina supaya
tak terbunuh Touman di masa depan!

157
00:08:45,760 --> 00:08:47,300
Janjiannya di sini?

158
00:08:47,570 --> 00:08:48,620
Ya.

159
00:08:49,440 --> 00:08:50,100
Eh?

160
00:08:59,280 --> 00:09:00,710
Betulan di sini?

161
00:09:00,780 --> 00:09:01,930
I-Iya.

162
00:09:06,680 --> 00:09:08,400
Orang-orangnya serem banget.

163
00:09:08,590 --> 00:09:12,010
Te-Tenang saja.
Ada aku di sini.

164
00:09:12,090 --> 00:09:14,620
Tapi, jangan jelalatan, ya.

165
00:09:15,390 --> 00:09:18,920
Mereka memakai jaket khas anak geng motor,
terus jumlahnya sebanyak ini?

166
00:09:19,050 --> 00:09:19,890
Oi!

167
00:09:21,040 --> 00:09:24,670
Siapa kau?! Ini bukan tontonan!
Pergi sana!

168
00:09:26,250 --> 00:09:29,420
- Siapa kau, bangsat?
- Kubunuh kau, goblok!

169
00:09:29,950 --> 00:09:32,750
Yah, aku cuma dipanggil kemari.

170
00:09:32,760 --> 00:09:36,200
Tahukah kau tempat apa ini, berengsek?!

171
00:09:36,330 --> 00:09:37,980
Ku-Kuil Musa-

172
00:09:38,000 --> 00:09:41,650
Siapa juga yang memanggilmu
di rapatnya Touman?!

173
00:09:41,660 --> 00:09:43,310
Jangan pakai kekerasan!

174
00:09:43,530 --> 00:09:44,010
Hah?

175
00:09:45,980 --> 00:09:49,480
(Mitsuya Takashi -
Kapten Divisi Kedua Geng Tokyo Manji)

176
00:09:47,140 --> 00:09:49,240
Jangan-jangan kau Takemichi?

177
00:09:49,680 --> 00:09:51,370
I-Iya.

178
00:09:52,370 --> 00:09:55,320
Kenapa kalian malah
menakuti tamunya Ketua?

179
00:09:55,500 --> 00:09:56,950
Ma-Maaf!

180
00:09:59,060 --> 00:10:00,750
Kamu baik-baik saja, Takemichi?

181
00:10:00,920 --> 00:10:01,820
Iya.

182
00:10:02,340 --> 00:10:03,290
Ikut aku.

183
00:10:03,540 --> 00:10:04,370
Eh?

184
00:10:04,490 --> 00:10:05,790
Oke, baik!

185
00:10:10,010 --> 00:10:11,810
Yo, Takemicchi.

186
00:10:13,700 --> 00:10:16,120
Maaf tiba-tiba memanggilmu kemari.

187
00:10:16,630 --> 00:10:19,330
Kenapa kau malah bawa cewekmu?

188
00:10:19,550 --> 00:10:20,930
Maaf.

189
00:10:21,240 --> 00:10:23,560
Aku enggak menyangka
bakal seramai ini.

190
00:10:23,780 --> 00:10:25,220
Ah, Hina.

191
00:10:25,690 --> 00:10:27,520
Maaf mengagetkanmu tempo hari.

192
00:10:27,630 --> 00:10:30,290
Ah, enggak apa-apa.
Bukan masalah, kok!

193
00:10:30,510 --> 00:10:33,780
Anu, aku juga minta maaf
soal waktu itu.

194
00:10:34,430 --> 00:10:35,430
Oi, Emma!

195
00:10:35,740 --> 00:10:36,810
Hadir!

196
00:10:36,920 --> 00:10:40,170
Dia ceweknya Takemichi,
jadi kau harus melindunginya!

197
00:10:40,360 --> 00:10:41,170
Eh?

198
00:10:43,510 --> 00:10:45,330
Oke, deh.

199
00:10:45,770 --> 00:10:46,400
Wah.

200
00:10:46,650 --> 00:10:47,730
Hah?!

201
00:10:48,400 --> 00:10:50,280
Yo, Mas Pengecut!

202
00:10:51,930 --> 00:10:54,090
Mas Pengecut itu maksudnya apa?

203
00:10:54,610 --> 00:10:57,100
Loh, kau kenal sama Emma?

204
00:10:57,310 --> 00:10:59,330
Bukan begitu, Hina!

205
00:10:59,410 --> 00:11:02,550
Bang Draken,
aku enggak ingat apa-apa!

206
00:11:02,740 --> 00:11:05,700
Bukannya kamu kabur setelah
lihat pakaian dalamku?

207
00:11:06,100 --> 00:11:09,860
Eh? Terjadi hal kayak begitu, ya?

208
00:11:09,970 --> 00:11:11,400
'Emangnya iya?

209
00:11:12,200 --> 00:11:14,500
Aku sama sekali
enggak ingat apa-apa, loh!

210
00:11:15,470 --> 00:11:17,370
Loh, kamu kenapa, Hina?

211
00:11:21,680 --> 00:11:23,380
Aku minta maaf.

212
00:11:24,000 --> 00:11:25,050
Bodo amat!

213
00:11:26,070 --> 00:11:27,260
Ngeri!

214
00:11:27,320 --> 00:11:30,380
Padahal kamu punya cewek kayak begitu,
tapi bisa-bisanya meladeni tawaranku.

215
00:11:30,460 --> 00:11:32,240
Tapi, jangan salah paham, ya.

216
00:11:32,720 --> 00:11:35,550
Aku enggak punya perasaan
apa-apa terhadapmu.

217
00:11:35,750 --> 00:11:36,510
Eh?

218
00:11:37,190 --> 00:11:40,370
Aku cuma ingin cepat dewasa.

219
00:11:42,170 --> 00:11:44,420
Dia sama sekali enggak tertarik padaku!

220
00:11:44,890 --> 00:11:47,450
Dia cuma tertarik sama
Mikey, motor, dan gelut.

221
00:11:48,340 --> 00:11:50,910
Kukira dia bakal sedikit marah.

222
00:11:51,970 --> 00:11:53,320
Oh, begitu.

223
00:11:53,690 --> 00:11:56,270
Dia ingin membuat Bang Draken cemburu.

224
00:11:56,860 --> 00:12:00,240
Selain itu, cewek memang sulit dipahami!

225
00:12:00,460 --> 00:12:01,450
Takemicchi!

226
00:12:01,580 --> 00:12:02,140
Ah.

227
00:12:02,330 --> 00:12:03,400
Sudah beres?

228
00:12:03,560 --> 00:12:05,690
Aku minta maaf telah
membuatmu menunggu!

229
00:12:06,100 --> 00:12:09,540
Ayo kumpul semuanya!
Rapat mau dimulai!

230
00:12:11,420 --> 00:12:13,740
Terima kasih kerja kerasnya, Ketua!

231
00:12:44,170 --> 00:12:45,500
Hebatnya.

232
00:12:45,760 --> 00:12:49,760
Suasananya langsung berubah saat
Bang Mikey berdiri di hadapan mereka.

233
00:12:50,390 --> 00:12:53,390
Inikah yang disebut Ketua Touman?

234
00:12:54,190 --> 00:12:56,860
Kita berkumpul untuk membahas soal Moebius.

235
00:12:57,080 --> 00:12:59,670
Kalau menyenggol kita,
bakalan jadi perseteruan besar.

236
00:12:59,970 --> 00:13:01,350
Moebius?

237
00:13:01,690 --> 00:13:03,270
Perseteruan itu apa?

238
00:13:03,550 --> 00:13:04,980
Aku baru tahu!

239
00:13:05,380 --> 00:13:06,560
Okelah.

240
00:13:06,960 --> 00:13:09,010
Berikan pendapat kalian!

241
00:13:11,920 --> 00:13:13,010
Sa-Sakit!

242
00:13:13,150 --> 00:13:13,900
Apa yang kau-

243
00:13:14,900 --> 00:13:16,000
Hah?

244
00:13:17,490 --> 00:13:18,880
Mau protes?

245
00:13:18,880 --> 00:13:20,880
Kau Hanagaki, 'kan?

246
00:13:20,980 --> 00:13:26,450
(Pehyan - Wakil Kapten
Divisi Ketiga Geng Tokyo Manji)

247
00:13:22,140 --> 00:13:26,660
Tampaknya waktu itu kau
meladeni Kiyomasa kami, 'kan?!

248
00:13:26,450 --> 00:13:30,280
(Pachin - Kapten Divisi Ketiga Geng Tokyo Manji)

249
00:13:27,630 --> 00:13:30,110
'Gimana caramu bayar
uang taruhannya, bangsat?

250
00:13:30,620 --> 00:13:32,650
U-Uang taruhan?

251
00:13:32,870 --> 00:13:34,190
Hentikanlah, Pa.

252
00:13:35,360 --> 00:13:39,160
Bukankah kita sudah sepakat kalau
judi sabung orang itu dianggap tiada ...

253
00:13:39,330 --> 00:13:42,240
... karena ulah Kiyomasa yang
seenaknya membawa nama Touman?

254
00:13:42,500 --> 00:13:46,330
Hah? Aku ini bego,
makanya enggak paham begituan!

255
00:13:46,460 --> 00:13:49,420
Otaknya Pachin itu sekecil
kutu air, berengsek!

256
00:13:49,540 --> 00:13:51,460
Kalau kagak paham,
ya jangan dibahas, tolol!

257
00:13:51,600 --> 00:13:53,150
Oi, Pa.

258
00:13:54,350 --> 00:13:55,590
Diamlah.

259
00:13:56,490 --> 00:13:58,010
Maaf, Draken!

260
00:13:58,520 --> 00:13:59,250
Cih.

261
00:14:02,680 --> 00:14:05,350
Maafkanlah dia, Takemicchi.

262
00:14:05,820 --> 00:14:07,940
Soalnya Pa sedang frustrasi.

263
00:14:09,640 --> 00:14:11,830
Mereka orang yang urakan, ya.

264
00:14:12,160 --> 00:14:15,010
Temannya Pa berkelahi dengan Moebius.

265
00:14:15,740 --> 00:14:17,400
Itulah penyebab perseteruan ini.

266
00:14:17,620 --> 00:14:18,280
Eh?

267
00:14:18,530 --> 00:14:19,970
Apa yang terjadi?

268
00:14:20,170 --> 00:14:24,690
Pemimpinnya Moebius yang
bernama Osanai berbuat onar.

269
00:14:25,680 --> 00:14:29,350
Temannya Pa dijadikan
samsak tinju oleh Moebius.

270
00:14:29,750 --> 00:14:33,870
Pacarnya yang bersamanya ikut disikat,
lalu uangnya dirampas.

271
00:14:33,920 --> 00:14:36,520
Kemudian, orang tua dan
saudaranya juga dihajar.

272
00:14:37,830 --> 00:14:39,000
Kejam banget.

273
00:14:39,340 --> 00:14:42,180
Moebius memang tim yang seperti itu.

274
00:14:42,690 --> 00:14:45,760
Mereka dua tahun di atas kami,
dan memegang wilayah Shinjuku.

275
00:14:45,960 --> 00:14:46,640
Eh?

276
00:14:47,010 --> 00:14:49,180
Bukannya Touman yang
memegang daerah ini?

277
00:14:49,400 --> 00:14:52,520
Touman memegang Shibuya,
kalau Shinjuku beda urusan.

278
00:14:52,780 --> 00:14:55,430
Lagian, kami ini masih tim baru.

279
00:14:55,770 --> 00:14:56,880
Oh, begitu.

280
00:14:57,090 --> 00:15:00,430
Di zaman ini, ada tim yang
lebih besar dari Touman, ya?

281
00:15:02,540 --> 00:15:04,380
Bagaimana, Pa?

282
00:15:05,580 --> 00:15:06,530
Sikat, 'gak?

283
00:15:08,320 --> 00:15:10,350
Mereka dua tahun di atas kita.

284
00:15:12,900 --> 00:15:15,760
Meski Touman tak bisa
membiarkan mereka begitu saja,

285
00:15:16,140 --> 00:15:18,490
anggota lain bakal kerepotan.

286
00:15:21,160 --> 00:15:22,580
Namun!

287
00:15:23,150 --> 00:15:25,100
Aku frustrasi, Mikey!

288
00:15:25,220 --> 00:15:27,370
Bukan itu yang kutanyakan.

289
00:15:27,930 --> 00:15:29,170
Sikat, nih?

290
00:15:30,110 --> 00:15:31,180
Atau kagak?

291
00:15:33,740 --> 00:15:37,720
Aku mau! Aku bahkan
mau membunuh mereka!

292
00:15:38,480 --> 00:15:39,240
Pastinya, ya.

293
00:15:39,360 --> 00:15:40,010
Eh?

294
00:15:44,680 --> 00:15:49,400
Apa ada orang yang menganggap Pa
merepotkan karena temannya dikeroyok?

295
00:15:51,360 --> 00:15:55,420
Apa masih ada yang mau diam saja,
padahal temannya Pa dikeroyok?!

296
00:15:56,880 --> 00:15:58,430
Tidak ada, 'kan?!

297
00:16:04,940 --> 00:16:07,080
AYO HANCURKAN MOEBIUS!

298
00:16:08,670 --> 00:16:12,610
Kita akan tawuran pada
3 Agustus saat Festival Musashi!

299
00:16:18,850 --> 00:16:20,520
3 Agustus?

300
00:16:21,560 --> 00:16:25,140
3 Agustus.
Selamatkan Ryuguji Ken.

301
00:16:26,000 --> 00:16:27,750
Itu hari kematian Draken!

302
00:16:29,520 --> 00:16:33,780
Kata Naoto, pada tanggal 3 Agustus,
Draken mati karena terlibat perseteruan ...

303
00:16:34,000 --> 00:16:35,970
... antara Kubu Mikey dan Kubu Draken.

304
00:16:36,620 --> 00:16:39,380
Tapi, saat aku kembali
ke 12 tahun lalu,

305
00:16:39,600 --> 00:16:42,810
perseteruan Touman dan
Moebius akan dimulai.

306
00:16:45,050 --> 00:16:46,420
Itu artinya ....

307
00:16:47,130 --> 00:16:49,890
Kepalaku enggak bisa mencernanya!

308
00:16:50,990 --> 00:16:52,950
Aku tercerahkan, Naoto!

309
00:16:53,760 --> 00:16:57,380
Aku akan menjadi pengawal Draken!

310
00:16:57,800 --> 00:16:58,410
Sip!

311
00:16:58,590 --> 00:17:00,480
Ini cara genius alaku.

312
00:17:01,120 --> 00:17:02,360
Pengawal?

313
00:17:02,800 --> 00:17:03,650
Ogah.

314
00:17:03,770 --> 00:17:05,119
'Makasih!

315
00:17:06,010 --> 00:17:07,560
Eh? Kau bilang apa?

316
00:17:07,819 --> 00:17:10,060
Pengawal itu merepotkan.

317
00:17:10,369 --> 00:17:12,270
Lagian, apa gunanya dirimu?

318
00:17:12,420 --> 00:17:13,880
Jangan sekasar itu, dong ....

319
00:17:14,440 --> 00:17:16,460
Misiku gagal seketika!

320
00:17:17,089 --> 00:17:20,740
Tapi, bukan aku namanya
kalau menyerah secepat itu!

321
00:17:20,880 --> 00:17:22,810
Rencana B.
Aku akan membuntutinya!

322
00:17:24,220 --> 00:17:25,790
Apa-apaan ini?!

323
00:17:26,880 --> 00:17:27,859
Mereka berantem?

324
00:17:27,920 --> 00:17:29,860
Selamanya takkan kumaafkan!

325
00:17:30,030 --> 00:17:30,760
Hah?

326
00:17:30,840 --> 00:17:32,490
Awal mula perseteruan internal?!

327
00:17:32,730 --> 00:17:34,680
Kagak ada benderanya!

328
00:17:38,210 --> 00:17:38,780
Eh?

329
00:17:39,170 --> 00:17:42,480
Aku antusias sama porsi bocah
karena ada benderanya!

330
00:17:42,770 --> 00:17:44,650
Maaf. Saya akan segera-

331
00:17:44,650 --> 00:17:47,320
Nih, Mikey. Ada benderanya.

332
00:17:48,980 --> 00:17:50,550
Kenchin memang hebat!

333
00:17:50,690 --> 00:17:51,240
Hah?

334
00:17:51,690 --> 00:17:53,300
Benderanya dari mana, tuh?

335
00:17:54,610 --> 00:17:55,900
Duh!

336
00:17:56,190 --> 00:17:57,520
Aku tidak tahan lagi!

337
00:17:57,610 --> 00:18:00,510
Apa, nih?
Apa mereka berantem?!

338
00:18:02,960 --> 00:18:04,760
Lah? Dia tidur?

339
00:18:04,950 --> 00:18:08,200
Cepatlah ubah perilakumu
yang habis makan tidur!

340
00:18:09,640 --> 00:18:11,990
Dasar. Apa boleh buat.

341
00:18:12,960 --> 00:18:16,850
Jadi, tingkah Bang Mikey
biasanya seperti itu, ya?

342
00:18:23,000 --> 00:18:25,240
Bang Draken hebat, ya.

343
00:18:25,580 --> 00:18:28,320
Soalnya tiap hari dia menopang
orang yang seperti itu.

344
00:18:29,080 --> 00:18:31,870
Tapi, kalau mereka berselisih ....

345
00:18:34,690 --> 00:18:36,610
Mikey, sudah sampai, nih.

346
00:18:37,200 --> 00:18:40,290
Eh? Ada perlu apa di tempat ini?

347
00:18:41,370 --> 00:18:42,760
Ada sedikit urusan.

348
00:18:45,340 --> 00:18:46,210
Siapa?

349
00:18:47,230 --> 00:18:48,850
Pacar temannya Pa.

350
00:18:50,860 --> 00:18:53,410
Itu penyebab perseteruan dengan Moebius.

351
00:18:54,320 --> 00:18:57,300
Katanya, dia sudah tak sadarkan diri
selama lima hari.

352
00:18:59,950 --> 00:19:02,310
Ada perlu apa kalian kemari?!

353
00:19:02,810 --> 00:19:05,460
Berani-beraninya kalian kemari!
Pulang sana!

354
00:19:05,580 --> 00:19:06,780
Ayah.

355
00:19:09,580 --> 00:19:10,890
Untuk apa?

356
00:19:10,960 --> 00:19:14,120
Karena salah sampah seperti kalian,
putriku nyaris mati!

357
00:19:14,420 --> 00:19:17,920
Kita tidak perlu membungkuk, Kenchin.
Toh, kita tidak salah.

358
00:19:18,070 --> 00:19:20,710
Lagian kenapa om-om ini menuduh kita?

359
00:19:20,770 --> 00:19:22,710
Dasar bajingan!

360
00:19:22,850 --> 00:19:27,230
Dengan bikin ribut di malam hari,
kalian sudah jadi sampah masyarakat!

361
00:19:27,320 --> 00:19:29,040
- Hentikanlah, Ayah.
- Hah?

362
00:19:29,310 --> 00:19:31,960
Kalian merepotkan dan melukai orang lain!

363
00:19:32,100 --> 00:19:35,770
Jangan pikir perbuatan jahat kalian bisa
dimaafkan sekalipun berubah saat dewasa nanti!

364
00:19:35,850 --> 00:19:37,950
Dasar bocah badung!

365
00:19:38,910 --> 00:19:41,180
Apa kau tidak tahu
lawan bicaramu itu siapa?!

366
00:19:41,780 --> 00:19:43,390
Woi! Apa yang kau lakukan?!

367
00:19:43,590 --> 00:19:45,790
Semuanya adalah tanggung jawab kami.

368
00:19:46,020 --> 00:19:46,700
Oi!

369
00:19:46,820 --> 00:19:50,660
Sekalipun sampah seperti kalian membungkuk,
memangnya putriku bisa kembali seperti dulu?!

370
00:19:50,680 --> 00:19:51,420
Hah?!

371
00:19:51,640 --> 00:19:53,230
Diamlah, Mikey.

372
00:19:54,000 --> 00:19:56,080
Perkataan Mikey ada benarnya.

373
00:19:56,560 --> 00:19:58,210
Mereka berdua tidak bersalah.

374
00:19:58,740 --> 00:20:02,520
Selama ini, putriku koma.

375
00:20:04,870 --> 00:20:06,110
Baik wajah,

376
00:20:06,960 --> 00:20:08,460
maupun tubuhnya,

377
00:20:09,290 --> 00:20:11,070
dipenuhi luka.

378
00:20:15,580 --> 00:20:16,770
Kenapa?

379
00:20:17,560 --> 00:20:20,230
Memangnya apa yang putriku
lakukan pada kalian?

380
00:20:24,880 --> 00:20:28,910
Anakku yang sebaik dan semanis itu ...

381
00:20:29,090 --> 00:20:32,760
... kini sekujur tubuhnya babak belur.

382
00:20:35,560 --> 00:20:37,040
Pulanglah.

383
00:20:37,830 --> 00:20:40,600
Jangan pernah muncul lagi di hadapan kami.

384
00:20:47,440 --> 00:20:49,300
Kita akan melawan Moebius.

385
00:20:49,980 --> 00:20:51,920
Masalah yang terjadi di dunia kita,

386
00:20:51,920 --> 00:20:54,180
kita sendirilah yang akan menuntaskannya.

387
00:20:54,830 --> 00:20:56,330
Di anggota geng kita pun,

388
00:20:56,480 --> 00:20:59,300
mereka juga punya keluarga
dan orang yang berharga.

389
00:21:00,590 --> 00:21:02,670
Jangan libatkan orang
yang tak ada hubungannya.

390
00:21:03,400 --> 00:21:05,700
Jangan membuat orang
di sekitar kita menangis.

391
00:21:06,760 --> 00:21:09,230
Kau tidak harus memiliki
kepala yang suka membungkuk.

392
00:21:09,940 --> 00:21:12,220
Cukup milikilah hati yang
peduli pada orang lain.

393
00:21:15,520 --> 00:21:17,430
Kenchin baik banget, ya.

394
00:21:18,580 --> 00:21:20,520
Maaf, Kenchin.

395
00:21:21,310 --> 00:21:22,700
Aku ...

396
00:21:23,740 --> 00:21:26,210
... bersyukur ada dirimu di sisiku.

397
00:21:28,160 --> 00:21:30,340
Tampaknya, aku mulai paham.

398
00:21:30,840 --> 00:21:34,820
Alasan Mikey berubah
sejak kematian Draken.

399
00:21:35,410 --> 00:21:39,710
Lalu kenapa 12 tahun kemudian,
Touman menjadi geng jahat.

400
00:21:41,190 --> 00:21:43,800
Draken tidak seharusnya mati.

401
00:21:44,650 --> 00:21:46,930
Draken adalah hatinya Mikey.

402
00:21:47,650 --> 00:21:49,660
Mereka saling melengkapi kekurangan.

403
00:21:52,270 --> 00:21:54,320
Aku jadi lapar, nih.

404
00:21:54,510 --> 00:21:57,140
Lah, padahal tadi baru makan.

405
00:21:57,320 --> 00:21:59,140
Tidur bikin lapar.

406
00:21:59,300 --> 00:22:01,020
Logika macam apa itu?

407
00:22:02,560 --> 00:22:03,800
Naoto!

408
00:22:04,990 --> 00:22:06,750
Mereka berdua tidak mungkin ...

409
00:22:06,900 --> 00:22:09,730
... membuat Touman terlibat
perseteruan internal!

410
00:22:21,040 --> 00:22:26,880
Dengan berjalan di sisimu yang
agak bau keringat

411
00:22:26,900 --> 00:22:29,790
itu sudah cukup bagiku

412
00:22:30,030 --> 00:22:35,810
Seraya dihantam oleh hujan tiba-tiba,

413
00:22:35,820 --> 00:22:39,320
kita berciuman di tengah dinginnya malam

414
00:22:41,220 --> 00:22:49,070
Kala aku berpaling, masihlah ada
diriku yang kerap tertawa

415
00:22:49,120 --> 00:22:50,250
Tolonglah!

416
00:22:50,270 --> 00:22:57,220
Hei, ayo menuju masa depan yang
tak mungkin terwujud!

417
00:22:57,260 --> 00:22:59,710
Bawalah aku sekarang juga

418
00:22:59,730 --> 00:23:01,720
ke dunia baru

419
00:23:01,730 --> 00:23:06,440
olehmu yang kusebut sebagai "pahlawanku"

420
00:23:06,440 --> 00:23:08,450
Harapan yang blak-blakan

421
00:23:08,470 --> 00:23:10,760
melampaui waktu yang terhenti

422
00:23:10,820 --> 00:23:15,710
"Tiada lagi yang kubutuhkan selainmu"

423
00:23:15,750 --> 00:23:23,590
Aku akan selalu bernapas di sini

424
00:23:29,930 --> 00:23:32,100
Hancurkan jarum yang bengkok

425
00:23:32,160 --> 00:23:34,400
dengan suara tegas

426
00:23:34,410 --> 00:23:36,810
lalu empaskan takdir!


